---
import { resolveBaseSegment } from "src/utils/navigation";
const url = `0;url=/${resolveBaseSegment()}/vi/`;
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="vi">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <title>Redirecting…</title>
        <meta http-equiv="refresh" content={url} />
        <link rel="canonical" href="/vi/" />
        <style>
            body {
                background-color: #f8fafc;
                color: #0f172a;
                font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
                display: flex;
                justify-content: center;
                align-items: center;
                height: 100vh;
                margin: 0;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 1.25rem;
                animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
            }
            a {
                color: #0073ff;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }
            @keyframes pulse {
                0%, 100% {
                    opacity: 1;
                }
                50% {
                    opacity: .5;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>
            Đang chuyển hướng... Nếu bạn không được chuyển hướng tự động, vui lòng truy cập <a href="/vi/">tại đây</a>.
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
